void* ptlrpc_async_args::pointer_arg[11]

Scratchpad for passing args to completion interpreter.

Users cast to the struct of their choosing, and CLASSERT that this is big enough. For _tons_ of context, OBD_ALLOC a struct and store a pointer to it here. The pointer_arg ensures this struct is at least big enough for that.
